==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Palp
<hw>Palp</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>palpare</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>palper</ets>.]</ety> <def>To have a distinct touch or feeling of;
to feel.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To bring a <qex>palp⟦egrave⟧d darkness o'er the earth</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Heywood.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Palpability</ent>⟦br⟧
